<div class="docs-section">
  <h2 class="docs-section__title">Default Header</h2>
  <p class="docs-section__description">The standard header for all public-facing pages. Its sticky position keeps navigation accessible as users scroll, and the glass-blur pill floats above page content without hard-blocking any layout. Use this variant whenever the page has a light or image background directly beneath the nav.</p>
  <div class="ds-preview ds-preview--warm" style="padding: 0; overflow: hidden; min-height: 80px;">
    <header class="header" style="position: relative; top: auto;">
      <div class="header__inner">
        <div class="header__pill">
          <a href="#" class="header__logo" aria-label="Regent's University London">
            <img src="/public/full-logo.svg" alt="Regent's University London" width="142" height="29">
          </a>
          <nav class="header__nav" aria-label="Main navigation">
            <a href="#" class="header__nav-link">Foundation</a>
            <a href="#" class="header__nav-link header__nav-link--active">Components</a>
            <a href="#" class="header__nav-link">Layouts</a>
            <a href="#" class="header__nav-link">Templates</a>
          </nav>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="docs-section">
  <h2 class="docs-section__title">With CTA Actions</h2>
  <p class="docs-section__description">Add a <code>.header__actions</code> slot when a persistent CTA — Apply Now, Log In — must remain visible at all times regardless of scroll position. Keep to a single button to avoid overloading the pill. Prefer the Small size to maintain the compact feel of the header.</p>
  <div class="ds-preview ds-preview--warm" style="padding: 0; overflow: hidden; min-height: 80px;">
    <header class="header" style="position: relative; top: auto;">
      <div class="header__inner">
        <div class="header__pill">
          <a href="#" class="header__logo" aria-label="Regent's University London">
            <img src="/public/full-logo.svg" alt="Regent's University London" width="142" height="29">
          </a>
          <nav class="header__nav" aria-label="Main navigation">
            <a href="#" class="header__nav-link">About</a>
            <a href="#" class="header__nav-link">Courses</a>
            <a href="#" class="header__nav-link">Research</a>
          </nav>
          <div class="header__actions">
            <a href="#" class="btn btn--primary-inverted btn--sm">Apply Now</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>
  </div>
</div>

